How very...

36
00:05:05,208 --> 00:05:07,375
...lame.

37
00:05:07,458 --> 00:05:08,125
[Excalibur]
Young lad...

38
00:05:08,208 --> 00:05:09,208
How are you called?

39
00:05:09,291 --> 00:05:12,041
Me...? Uh, well,
my name is Ox Ford-- 

40
00:05:12,125 --> 00:05:12,791
[Excalibur]
Fool!

41
